{"tid":1533698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位善長人翁，宣明會咁多醜聞，捐款又送中，你仲捐得落手？","createTime":"2019-09-02T19:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:19.000Z","uid":38376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2621aedc70b64566b9795f1c4a9178ad141ec8","tid":1533698,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:31:21.000Z","msg":"[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">各位善長人翁，宣明會高層每年支取6百萬年薪，你哋嘅善款真係比佢哋每年搭飛機周圍去，食好西<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWYg8SV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWYg8SV.jpg&h=d0ea8198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且，中國接受嘅善款有超過6成係黎自香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ns9TrKJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fns9TrKJ.jpg&h=4207ca52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲爆咁多醜聞<br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: blue;\">宣明會承認貪污，及要求女災民以性服務換糧食援助<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309906&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgRs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=eef13a12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309906&h=b581ec46\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309906</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/mobile/bknint-20180218150855747-0218_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180218%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180218150855747-0218_17011_001.html&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgRs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=2bee5b12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/mobile/bknint-20180218150855747-0218_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/wo/647271/日報-國際-宣明會再爆醜聞-職員要求災民以性換糧\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.s